368
00:24:14,871 --> 00:24:17,290
- What's that?
- What? My sister.

369
00:24:18,207 --> 00:24:19,834
Oh, Bo-mi...

370
00:24:44,150 --> 00:24:45,276
This is me.

371
00:24:48,154 --> 00:24:49,363
