476
00:31:22,548 --> 00:31:24,258
Yu-jeong.

477
00:31:26,844 --> 00:31:28,387
We should finish our talk.

478
00:31:28,721 --> 00:31:30,681
Out of my way. Maybe later.

479
00:31:32,641 --> 00:31:33,809
