481
00:31:38,981 --> 00:31:42,860
Tonight, there will be
a big fire in our house.

482
00:31:44,320 --> 00:31:46,363
So sexy!

483
00:31:55,748 --> 00:31:56,999
Bo-mi.

484
00:31:57,082 --> 00:31:58,959
You can sit here.

485
00:31:59,043 --> 00:32:00,419
Yes, there.

486
00:32:09,553 --> 00:32:11,096
