494
00:32:44,797 --> 00:32:45,798
Yes.

495
00:32:45,881 --> 00:32:47,132
From what?

496
00:32:47,216 --> 00:32:48,217
From you?

497
00:32:49,802 --> 00:32:50,928
I think so.

498
00:32:51,011 --> 00:32:52,012
Sort of.

499
00:32:53,347 --> 00:32:57,226
